name: autocomplete_zipcodes_zip4
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool autocomplete_usa.
Tool description: USA Address, City, Zip code - Zip4, Zip code Autocomplete
API description: Fetches autocomplete suggestions for USA Zip+4 zip codes using the provided zipcode and API key.

zipcode.description: The base ZIP code for which to fetch autocomplete suggestions.
